Package: simulatR
Type: Package
Title: Simulate the evolution of species across regions
Version: 0.1.0
Date: 2022-11-08
Authors@R: person("Thomas", "Smith", role = c("aut","cre"), email = "thomas.smith@earth.ox.ac.uk") 
Maintainer: Thomas Smith <thomas.smith@earth.ox.ac.uk>
Description: A flexible simulation framework for simulating speciation, extirpation, extinction, and dispersal across space and time. The package includes functions for generating heterogeneous landscapes and simulating the evolution of species across them.
